				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\sigma _\epsilon ^2$$\end{document}σϵ2 is common within the population. The variance of the true parameter, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
